# Project: Spring Boot AI Agent Application

## General

- This is a Spring Boot AI Workflow application
- Uses Java 21 as development language
- Integrates with Spring AI for AI model integration
- Follows Domain-Driven Design (DDD) architecture

## File Structure

- src/main/java/io/github/samzhu/studio/: Main source code
- application/: Application layer code
- configuration/: Configuration related code
- exception/: Exception handling code
- infrastructures/: Infrastructure layer code
- models/: Domain model code

## Coding Standards

- 符合 DDD 的分層架構
- 清晰的關注點分離
- 容易擴展新的 LLM 提供商
- 便於維護和測試
- 遵循單一職責原則
- Use PascalCase for class names
- Use camelCase for methods and variables

## Architecture Patterns

- Use Strategy pattern for different AI model implementations
- Use Factory pattern for AI model instance creation
- Use Adapter pattern for different output formats
- Use Domain Events for system integration
- Follow SOLID principles in design